.SH "NAME"
vfs_full_audit - record Samba VFS operations in the system log
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP 1
vfs objects = full_audit
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
This VFS module is part of the
\fBsamba\fR(7)
suite\.
.PP
The
vfs_full_audit
VFS module records selected client operations to the system log using
\fBsyslog\fR(3)\.
